{"type": "article", "id": 49088, "title": "把天花板和廊柱的细节做成凳子，而且是软软的那种｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-01-10T23:14:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 31325, "name": "Chilewich"}, {"id": 46955, "name": "agus kim"}, {"id": 46956, "name": "Almerich"}, {"id": 46957, "name": "Wang & Söderström"}, {"id": 46958, "name": "Ian Berry"}, {"id": 25263, "name": "Nynke Koster"}, {"id": 46959, "name": "Gal Rozov"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 168, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180111071327TADwp9EcK5kbzNYs.jpg", "contents": "<p oncecleanhtml=\"true\">「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Limited-edition Excavation Series by Wang &amp; Söderström</h3><p>总部位于哥本哈根的艺术设计工作室 Wang &amp; Söderström 的新作，是一系列名为 Excavation 的限量版花瓶，与其合作的是纽约公司 Unique Board 。它们经由 3D 打印技术支撑，图案来自于计算机算法。</p><p>最初 Excavation 系列定位于艺术品创作，但在决定其形状后，设计师发现它们非常适合用作花瓶，下半部分形成基座，上半部分插入鲜花。不同部分采用了不同的材料和技术，顶部由石膏制成，饰面是经算法而得的图案。粉色，烧焦质感的橙红色以及深绿色等搭配不同的有机形状，为这组花瓶更添艺术感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110174609BgKtk2hqczsXIYSo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110174612Mh4UGP1bfRJFZm6v.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110174613Ojx4qzck3QhlaHeu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599831\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110174617qJUPl56ECKsOXuQS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.071912\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110174619FvtDfdbS7hyMgUpX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110174621MGbFDQU9iwKYxAgu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110174632tRHDaC7oUiTLysSd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.185702\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>Moon minimalist collection of lighting by agus kim for Almerich</h3><p>Moon 极简系列灯饰是西班牙品牌 Almerich 的新作，出自巴伦西亚设计工作室 agus kim 之手，灵感源自满月时的月光，这也是其名字的来源。不对称的固定支架上装着大小不一的灯球，非透明质感让其看上去像是地球仪，感觉像是一组太阳系里的行星。Moon 系列包括落地灯、台灯和吊灯，是能够为居家环境创造艺术氛围的灯饰。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110174703DStCQwsvbABujkyJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.762000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110174703iZbpyUX2MBrVCH6e.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.846000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110174703cjOxrp9KJkt4hag8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.885000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110174703v5sz3W0nLNqFmlyp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110174705HUQaDS9q3XuExkG2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.735000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>FoldiMate by Gal Rozov </h3><p>FoldiMate 自动折衣机是懒得叠衣服族群的救星。它可以自动将衣服折叠、蒸汽防皱、喷洒香水或是消毒，省时方便，解决很多整理衣物的烦恼。FoldiMate 宽 71 厘米、高 81 厘米，深 79 厘米，重量 30 公斤，不会很占地儿。</p><p>折叠衣服的时间不到 10 秒，蒸汽除皱功能需要花费 20 至 30 秒，处理每件衣服的时间不到一分钟。使用者只需要将晒干的衣服按照顺序夹在机器上，启动后衣物会自动送进机器折叠，其他功能也是自由选择的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=a0531wydg3q&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\"></iframe> </figure> </div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801101747583zsh5fuGQYaxLrvB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110174757ZOqoebJQi4rTYj06.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.601467\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110174757MwE5f03TguzpPF2v.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110174758svpVFN3cO182KqU4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.207824\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110174807yWiNgKcpZ9UbzV2t.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.831296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>Fragments of Time by Nynke Koster</h3><p>东京都庭园美术馆正在进行一场名为 Decoration Never Dies, Anyway 的展览，荷兰设计师 Nynke Koster 的 Fragments of Time 项目是其中一部分。她将装饰艺术的一些标志性形式运用于橡胶凳子的设计中，比如巴洛克式的天花板、新艺术风格的建筑物细节或是新古典主义时期的建筑细节等等。</p><p>Nynke Koster 喜欢观察建筑的装饰细节，这是她设计这一系列凳子的灵感来源，通过模具铸造的装饰细节，加上柔软弹性好的凳面，赋予了凳子一种俏皮的性格。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110174840DKiZBr73LysWF95g.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.221271\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110174840Y8U1TEulVwiXKq0b.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.169927\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110174841i56NeAdZIqYk4EFW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110174842AYa4o1vsXmbQkD9K.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110174845r9w0CKzS61vfYgoF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.960880\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110174845JsH8P3NFKqSc7BWu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.993888\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110174848p9NC1HWVJbMUoag3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.003667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>Colorful Spring/Summer 2018 Collection by Chilewich</h3><p>美国知名餐垫品牌 Chilewich 推出 2018 春夏系列新品，对于如何扮靓餐桌，Chilewich 总是有各种办法，新系列从纱线的颜色、编织技法以及纹理设计方面皆有创新，尤其是纱线的色调，灵感源自春夏花园以及时令水果的色彩。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018011017493653n9xzPL8aCFUcRl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Basketweave 款式</figcaption> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110175023hyNgPW1DQf5k2eGU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Color Tempo 款式</figcaption> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110175051NpWIbwknm8HO41eE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.807031\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Float 款式</figcaption> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110175136ogOWIHpDzK4iGQ2C.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Glow 款式</figcaption> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110175222kTrUxiXOwqaNMvtl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Heather Shag 款式</figcaption> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110175254zA9FxqYkuopKr4Nl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Honeycomb 款式</figcaption> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110175322ndPzKDxqXYvOSlhk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Market Fringe 款式</figcaption> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801101754150och9VMWnJfUx3zv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Mini Basketweave 款式</figcaption> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110175450ARvB0x7TiwVG8kMW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Mosaic 款式</figcaption> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110175638yQApV5hocURMimtD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.803906\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Selvedge 款式</figcaption> </figure></div><h3>Secret Garden by Ian Berry</h3><p>在纽约儿童艺术博物馆，艺术家 Ian Berry 推出最新装置“秘密花园”（Secret Garden）。牛仔布是 Ian Berry 的创作主材，从玫瑰、仙人掌、紫藤到菊花等花卉植物，皆由牛仔布制成。</p><p>但最抓人眼球的是从天花板上垂吊下来的数百根藤蔓和树叶，定义了整个空间的基调。据称艺术家是受到童年经常在户外玩耍的记忆的启发，意识到现在的小孩很缺乏于大自然近距离接触的机会，创造了这个秘密花园，展览将持续到 4 月。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110175723dr2lgnhzVIMTKpYG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666364\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801101757244Q8a27RDUz1yYiN3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.797273\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110175725OpfTWKvAmV6JxlIt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110175729Y4wdUas0PzW5NMnx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666364\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110175731Ptm2wosD97FIN5KV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110175732NXbstjAHnquIEvKU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.560909\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div>"}